{"tid":29479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【軍事】愛沙尼亞開發無人小型戰車","createTime":"2016-12-08T14:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T00:59:06.000Z","uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"791782caa4b5d9b82f072d14c1f60dadafdbd701","tid":29479,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"【愛沙尼亞開發無人小型戰車】<br />\n<br />\n軍備發展追求「無人化」，即是盡量以機械代替士兵上前線，空中無人機已被多國納入軍備，那麼陸上作戰又如何？<br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞一間軍事企業，就開發了一種無人小型戰車，近日與當地軍方合作首次執行實彈試驗。<br />\n<br />\n影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/596510643874341/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F596510643874341%2F&d=qkK6BSb8oTDgM2Fg%2BRYRt4scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=fa293ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/596510643874341/</a><br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞為了強化本國軍工業的國際競爭率，其Milrem公司不僅將自家的「履帶混合模組化步兵系統」(Tracked Hybrid Modular Infantry System，THeMIS)推銷給愛沙尼亞軍方，更開始將觸角伸進國際市場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://main.dtmdatabase.com/Upload_File/images/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF/20161113/MilremUGV3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmain.dtmdatabase.com%2FUpload_File%2Fimages%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%2F20161113%2FMilremUGV3.jpg&h=f6a36a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>THeMIS高度模組化的設計，能隨著使用者需要，快速地更換中央承載模塊的配置，例如貨架、擔架或機械手臂等，同時也可以如圖中裝載遙控武器站，並搭載足以自衛或威力偵查的武裝。<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n其中，愛沙尼亞首款地面無人載具；「THeMIS 」正是Milrem當前最得意的作品，它整體採取模組化設計，可將全載具區分為三大塊，分別是左、右履帶模塊以及中央的乘載模塊，為了節省空間，柴/電發動機藏在右模塊中，而電瓶皆藏在左模塊之中，本體重850公斤，酬載可達750公斤，最高時速在25~35公里之間，並可單靠電池持續運作8小時，其中央乘載模塊能換裝貨籃、擔架、機械手臂甚至遙控武器站等各項裝備，其變體甚至高達12種，例如它能搭載一具新加坡STK生產的ADDER遙控武器站，並足以搭載一挺重機槍作為自衛或威力偵查所用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://main.dtmdatabase.com/Upload_File/images/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF/20161113/family.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmain.dtmdatabase.com%2FUpload_File%2Fimages%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%2F20161113%2Ffamily.jpg&h=44f327db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>如圖所見，Milrem將THeMIS設定可依照需求改裝成12種不同版本，其高度模組化程度可見一班。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://main.dtmdatabase.com/Upload_File/images/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF/20161113/testing.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmain.dtmdatabase.com%2FUpload_File%2Fimages%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%2F20161113%2Ftesting.jpg&h=111ea4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>目前THeMIS已經送交愛沙尼亞軍方實施測試，可注意到的是遙控人員手中並沒有拿著複雜的遙控器，而是一具以PS遊戲機遙控器改裝的操縱介面，對於年輕世代而言十分容易上手。</em>"},{"pid":"a0f6a00c1708e52b0760bd8782a30b7ae19684cd","tid":29479,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"Metal gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88357a15e871ecaebd4dd6c3dcd1bc40d613c11d","tid":29479,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"淨用電池補級唔方便應該用混能好d"},{"pid":"b3522fdb0f49d04d9cfaca5cf03938e6b6a3d9fb","tid":29479,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"買部嚟香港玩下! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6b4fa57442eb313dd5055fae0ebe3033401b6e","tid":29479,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef47b401abb21345b83da77ab021ece6ac7b952","tid":29479,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:52:12.000Z","msg":"打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e5abc7395deac85015192848d3e5e4753dbec0","tid":29479,"uid":6